Huang lab (黃憲松實驗室)























HUANGLAB
黃憲松實驗室


神經發育與神經表觀遺傳學實驗室
Laboratory Of Neurodevelopment And Neuroepigenetics
Laboratory Of
Neurodevelopment And Neuroepigenetics












           







About
We are interested in investigating neurodevelopment and neuroepigenetics with multidisciplinary approaches. We hope we can identify novel therapeutics for neurological and psychiatric disorders through our research.
我們實驗室利用不同的方法，來研究神經發育與神經表觀遺傳學，希望我們的研究，能夠找出治療神經和精神疾病的新策略。


 

